{"tid":316474,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[畫畫愛好者的經歷]2014年我畫咗個角色，冇乜人睇但我依然繼續畫","createTime":"2017-07-10T17:59:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-03T02:36:58.000Z","uid":75427,"like":78,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"da13c6155d5eb46cec6d96b5ea4a757728f576ba","tid":316474,"uid":75427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T17:59:02.000Z","msg":"唔好屌我咩臨近書展黎宣傳，我從來冇用我呢隻角色做商業野<br />\n我唔會話自己係藝術家/插畫師/圖文畫家等等，<br />\n啊豬啊狗都叫自己做 xx家/xx師，侮辱咗個專業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個range 唔應該係咁細的<br />\n言歸正轉，2014年聖誕節有一晚我好唔開心，唔知做乜好，就係高登開咗個帖幫人畫歌詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家睇返居然咁嘅畫功都可以開足三個post，真係好神奇 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/11/004906_47d0caa21d5cca89a1d382162de24553.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F11%2F004906_47d0caa21d5cca89a1d382162de24553.jpg&h=4195490b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/11/005232_11b3780268003541d21e534878996c65.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F11%2F005232_11b3780268003541d21e534878996c65.jpg&h=3e4283ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/11/005310_c95da6c1949a2e007c0b386d0ff1eacd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F11%2F005310_c95da6c1949a2e007c0b386d0ff1eacd.jpg&h=806a0bdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n畫吓畫吓主角開始似返啲樣，如果參考整容進化圖的話，依家應該係2.0<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/11/005646_698c056b2d0e50da79be2fa1e74ba758.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F11%2F005646_698c056b2d0e50da79be2fa1e74ba758.jpg&h=bc0fe6bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係高登畫歌詞大約畫咗5個月咗右，期間當然會係自己個FB page 到畫自己嘅一啲諗法啦~<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/11/011050_4c5c3098f6c4661365b8d752eb9c9e84.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F11%2F011050_4c5c3098f6c4661365b8d752eb9c9e84.jpg&h=bc2f9263&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/11/011157_9d9a5a3d49b9cd592085303b0062c0c1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F11%2F011157_9d9a5a3d49b9cd592085303b0062c0c1.jpg&h=b290b8f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當時係FB，有好多人都叫我開IG，咁我又開埋~<br />\n當時個FB page，啱啱開幾個月大約得二千人like ，裏面全部都係高登巴絲又或者佢地啲朋友，<br />\n因為我冇同我自己現實上嘅朋友講過我有開page呢一件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/11/011739_accd982a6e3fe5cd0c6bdbadda0c1d58.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F11%2F011739_accd982a6e3fe5cd0c6bdbadda0c1d58.jpg&h=eeafbff0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/11/011758_36d8c25505d555f8e0304c806b8b4d7c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F11%2F011758_36d8c25505d555f8e0304c806b8b4d7c.jpg&h=0fc13895&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/11/011843_6afef823905ee7bdf63f92b90cafefdc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F11%2F011843_6afef823905ee7bdf63f92b90cafefdc.jpg&h=b8f62da9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個時候，你會發現隻野個樣已經進化到3.0<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/11/012004_6abdf9b550be4401916acf882cf421dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F11%2F012004_6abdf9b550be4401916acf882cf421dd.jpg&h=e92341ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/11/012027_d3f0254e11c09c195c601a5a597b70df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F11%2F012027_d3f0254e11c09c195c601a5a597b70df.jpg&h=bc4be8c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n半年過去，我係到諗點解要同一樣野又放上FB之餘 ，又放上ＩＧ？我決定執咗個fb page佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ，然後到現在我個IG follower都唔夠以前多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過我嗰時個心態係有個地方俾我自己廢UP，因為我唔想係我本身真人圈子入面放負能量，一啲都唔似我平時形象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/11/012423_f785b4f74faffef2f4ea88a4107cde17.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F11%2F012423_f785b4f74faffef2f4ea88a4107cde17.jpg&h=55002ac8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n搬家去IG後，時間一野跳到去12月聖誕節，咁就一年了，嗰時IG入面都幾熱鬧，平時出個post都有 二三百個like，大家都係到留言同我傾計同Tag朋友黎睇，咁我見聖誕就整啲聖誕卡派街坊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  印象中好似寄咗五十幾六十張吧<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/11/013316_4a400989708866525162077e2428c86d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F11%2F013316_4a400989708866525162077e2428c86d.jpg&h=f5e312eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n畫佢已經成為咗我個習慣，平時聽到有咩歌詞有感觸就畫、有咩想法亦畫<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/11/013835_3a2c0852360b2a7a0144042f63138fa7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F11%2F013835_3a2c0852360b2a7a0144042f63138fa7.jpg&h=50b70ab7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/11/013846_bd19d6603980b287b09699b756b8493c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F11%2F013846_bd19d6603980b287b09699b756b8493c.jpg&h=55d254a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/11/013958_89840bd0a033fa63f6d493d088b95354.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F11%2F013958_89840bd0a033fa63f6d493d088b95354.jpg&h=e0ba488d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好多圖其實都係同我自己講緊，所以少人關注我都有乜所謂<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/11/014116_83cafcaaa4fb5c873c61da9b570f97f4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F11%2F014116_83cafcaaa4fb5c873c61da9b570f97f4.jpg&h=e9e74d3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n三年黎佢可以話記載住我嘅經歷，見證住我嘅轉變<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/11/014356_9e33a758048d6057cb956605eb66bedd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F11%2F014356_9e33a758048d6057cb956605eb66bedd.jpg&h=829199c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/11/014406_079e71c1fed59852a03f5c14783530e8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F11%2F014406_079e71c1fed59852a03f5c14783530e8.jpg&h=bb85bcdd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/11/014415_f64d1a295957917375805af32d774718.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F11%2F014415_f64d1a295957917375805af32d774718.jpg&h=598d50a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/11/014519_6069f17b73331ff49dbfb47584b8940c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F11%2F014519_6069f17b73331ff49dbfb47584b8940c.jpg&h=be585b3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n曾經迎合讀者口味，畫好多友情同愛情野，的而且確可以吸引到人黎FOLLOW，<br />\n但我冇繼續選擇呢一條路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  到依家已經冇乜人睇我出post了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/11/015021_2aba58dd0deb6c4b0a9e281aa6f1db74.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F11%2F015021_2aba58dd0deb6c4b0a9e281aa6f1db74.jpg&h=06a98450&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/11/015033_eec1f20585f2738451813aa34bd0f566.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F11%2F015033_eec1f20585f2738451813aa34bd0f566.jpg&h=1413507c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢已經成為咗我嘅心靈雞湯<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/11/015508_0194385d29628eba039f9b26bce47e69.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F11%2F015508_0194385d29628eba039f9b26bce47e69.jpg&h=f1743fac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我知自己畫嘅野點解會有乜人留意，但我唔會改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後想同大家講，堅持做自己想做嘅野啦!!"},{"pid":"6dd3be19c2c93996fc1f6b5e6a52cbeafcf0e810","tid":316474,"uid":75427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T18:02:55.000Z","msg":"有見過我呢隻野嘅人或者有FOLLOW開嘅巴絲打，歡迎say 個 hi ~~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61343567f9248c2f3b6e20820eb669f81eef51b8","tid":316474,"uid":54555,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T18:12:24.000Z","msg":"第一次見呢隻野，好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b74d8ccfa8c270994158c73445744a939dc51a6a","tid":316474,"uid":75427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T18:22:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第一次見呢隻野，好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n存在感=0 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d685fbe28f6a7b3cc30575112fee133cce34b241","tid":316474,"uid":69256,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T18:40:51.000Z","msg":"我鍾意1.0<img src=\"/assets