 /><br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"806d3919a8d15ef8c1df080b3923b084697e78a0","tid":316474,"uid":54812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T17:47:42.000Z","msg":"幾得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15e15c8142733f378d2e027f10d5e9f9bba52197","tid":316474,"uid":79442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T17:51:35.000Z","msg":"幾得意，我諗你要努力宣傳下"},{"pid":"2e4b59a00ce5d9b21495d2ca929a7da0575fb477","tid":316474,"uid":75427,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T17:56:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第一次見，得意wor！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我畫到依家都覺得佢好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  只係無奈我畫啲內容吸引唔到人，黎黎去去都係講緊自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d53eaa92737b7b9b374f32e5ccd200a38b9ff1c","tid":316474,"uid":75427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T17:58:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我有follow ig 一直有睇架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打，雖然我唔知你係邊個，但有好多舊面孔一個一個咁消失我都覺得好唏噓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b37684f1fffa6a8e99546c838fa1bc1b0c24a43d","tid":316474,"uid":75427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T17:59:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n希望你睇到佢之後個心有一絲溫暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  多謝你"},{"pid":"bfdf745387b82c8d514186de8580124193fa7104","tid":316474,"uid":73604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T18:02:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>第一次見，得意wor！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我畫到依家都覺得佢好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  只係無奈我畫啲內容吸引唔到人，黎黎去去都係講緊自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得每個人對於畫嘅睇法都有唔同，都有自己嘅想像空間。<br />\n同一幅畫嘅背後，配合唔同人嘅生活經歷可能有唔同嘅感受。唔好太介懷啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f5c5ed14ea67bdf992d3cd768d3aa189af142b2","tid":316474,"uid":75427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T18:04:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾得意，我諗你要努力宣傳下</blockquote><br />\n我一直個信念就係做好自己人地就會欣賞，但我依家發現唔係咁簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果想多啲人睇到真係要努力宣傳，以前人數不斷增長係因為讀者們都tag 佢地朋友入黎睇我啲畫，我以為keep 住咁好快就多人睇，點知慢慢就越黎越少人留言回覆tag 朋友，點知過去一年follow 人數居然倒退負增長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f76593861de180b4113500e8e461773303a6f6af","tid":316474,"uid":65587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T18:08:13.000Z","msg":"有科勞開<br />\n巴打 繼續加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d342a613379d3e747aa4e60ae343adfbed1e6bd6","tid":316474,"uid":75427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T18:09:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>第一次見，得意wor！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我畫到依家都覺得佢好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  只係無奈我畫啲內容吸引唔到人，黎黎去去都係講緊自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得每個人對於畫嘅睇法都有唔同，都有自己嘅想像空間。<br />\n同一幅畫嘅背後，配合唔同人嘅生活經歷可能有唔同嘅感受。唔好太介懷啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都係o架，唔同嘅生活經驗一定會影響人對事同物嘅睇法，而我絕對冇可能迎合晒所有人，所以都keep 住當心情日記咁post 圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\nbtw 巴打個名，係咪睇射雕英雄傳所以改到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23073c5fd1c8020dbb47e00b175a61fe16bad879","tid":316474,"uid":75427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T18:12:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有科勞開<br />\n巴打 繼續加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 他鄉遇故知，多謝你"},{"pid":"2d7b02b7256773406e083416ef7b152a97990a5f","tid":316474,"uid":75427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T18:26:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73acf614bc81f0b446e37a53ab9690ad2ac30877","tid":316474,"uid":17279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T18:32:16.000Z","msg":"離一離題 絲打啲人像畫好犀利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好想有你一成功力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b0e7f10392d074f18acfce4a765ceae72bf5505","tid":316474,"uid":24904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T19:26:15.000Z","msg":"舊登已開始支持<br />\n一直覺得你啲圖好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n繼續努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea900150fcf7c8be3c1f1b5cb23a3ab840e55b91","tid":316474,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T20:12:21.000Z","msg":"點解可以咁得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n擺自己IG上黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">ghostandgo.art</span></span>"},{"pid":"c254e90929317ea3c02ea0d265c17b083e45400f","tid":316474,"uid":75427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T04:57:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>離一離題 絲打啲人像畫好犀利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好想有你一成功力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係巴打啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n如果想畫人像畫，首先要熟識人頭部結構先，起碼就算畫得唔似但畫出黎都會似一個正常人，乜都唔理剩係照住相片練習成效會冇咁好，畢竟只係copy and paste<br />\n建議睇吓書~ <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.alexhays.com/loomis/Andrew%20Loomis%20-%20Drawing%20the%20Head%20and%20Hands.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.alexhays.com%2Floomis%2FAndrew%2520Loomis%2520-%2520Drawing%2520the%2520Head%2520and%2520Hands.pdf&d=9ky%2BgztbjGp%2BB9QNofxjDAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=aa3ab6d3\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.alexhays.com/loomis/Andrew%20Loomis%20-%20Drawing%20the%20Head%20and%20Hands.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"8a9090f1e7e4bfd5161226d9c2f531fcdd5d8f18","tid":316474,"uid":75427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T05:00:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>舊登已開始支持<br />\n一直覺得你啲圖好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n繼續努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你以前係咪都叫綿花糖，我有啲印象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多謝支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cc832e626fcd785ec89cb016cb6996bc8d6ad30","tid":316474,"uid":75427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T05:01:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解可以咁得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n擺自己IG上黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">ghostandgo.art</span></span></blockquote><br />\n我見啲圖都有晒水印，廢事咁hardsell啦～<br />\nthankyou<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab09ef70e8baa90f791b882d12af225d78186c3f","tid":316474,"uid":125341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T05:06:20.000Z","msg":"好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即刻follow 左<br />\n巴打加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c39bf7c709c5c7e399d386cc4f0ea46ebbc450f","tid":316474,"uid":75427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T05:57:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即刻follow 左<br />\n巴打加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  永不放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ce52ea2b7176f88f6549420df437ffa2bad5aa7","tid":316474,"uid":75427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T06:59:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8882ad23ab356d748a80d83b0cdd15d57d5f1169","tid":316474,"uid":75427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T07:39:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8e103915f6abe7b7a923b648b27b56588ae345f","tid":316474,"uid":17279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T08:09:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>離一離題 絲打啲人像畫好犀利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好想有你一成功力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係巴打啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n如果想畫人像畫，首先要熟識人頭部結構先，起碼就算畫得唔似但畫出黎都會似一個正常人，乜都唔理剩係照住相片練習成效會冇咁好，畢竟只係copy and paste<br />\n建議睇吓書~ <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.alexhays.com/loomis/Andrew%20Loomis%20-%20Drawing%20the%20Head%20and%20Hands.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.alexhays.com%2Floomis%2FAndrew%2520Loomis%2520-%2520Drawing%2520the%2520Head%2520and%2520Hands.pdf&d=9ky%2BgztbjGp%2BB9QNofxjDAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=aa3ab6d3\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.alexhays.com/loomis/Andrew%20Loomis%20-%20Drawing%20the%20Head%20and%20Hands.pdf</a></blockquote><br />\n原來係巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋想問下你練咗幾多年結構先畫成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aec928fe06c7120c3ce82002beba093b2f4fc3e6","tid":316474,"uid":75427,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T09:24:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n原來係巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋想問下你練咗幾多年結構先畫成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我正式學畫畫就三年（唔係專學人像畫），同埋我係知道咗就算，直接應用係我嘅畫上面，所以要答你練咗幾耐結構答唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n結構你睇下我上面本書啲圖，明咗就得，唔睇晒全本書都得，又話者係google 搵人像素描結構之類嘅野睇吓，google 搵藝用解剖又得，但其實我素描能力都好弱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n最主要係理解個結構，所以你會見到啲人學畫人會畫頭骨，又會畫下頭骨+面部肌肉組織，例如知道咗眉骨突，眼窩凹，顴骨突起，咁畫人像嗰時就要用線條/明暗/排線等手法表現到呢啲特點出黎， 然後又要睇啲小結構啦，就好似鼻孔係咪單統畫個圓形就得呢？照鏡睇下自已個鼻，鼻頭同鼻翼之間點樣互相連結呢？ 又例如眼，細心啲睇你會見到上眼簾會包住下眼簾。畫畫隨咗多畫之外，重要多看，睇到先會畫得到"},{"pid":"e9e14a5a545b1e4e22bbf75d163a0492b686e040","tid":316474,"uid":3342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T09:44:44.000Z","msg":"1.0正d<br />\n同埋希望堅持到唔好咁多情情愛愛"},{"pid":"24a073aaf03ca832652f1af10ce9fa4ff6f12058","tid":316474,"uid":75427,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T10:07:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1.0正d<br />\n同埋希望堅持到唔好咁多情情愛愛</blockquote><br />\n1.0邊到吸引到你？？<br />\n我會依住自己個心去畫畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  又唔係靠呢啲野搵食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d21e3f62288e28a18fbfdb21d18f3af0e37b5bc3","tid":316474,"uid":75427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T13:53:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed9ac9e4b674129fb060ec2c4abc07c534c42f8b","tid":316474,"uid":73604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T15:36:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>第一次見，得意wor！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我畫到依家都覺得佢好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  只係無奈我畫啲內容吸引唔到人，黎黎去去都係講緊自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得每個人對於畫嘅睇法都有唔同，都有自己嘅想像空間。<br />\n同一幅畫嘅背後，配合唔同人嘅生活經歷可能有唔同嘅感受。唔好太介懷啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都係o架，唔同嘅生活經驗一定會影響人對事同物嘅睇法，而我絕對冇可能迎合晒所有人，所以都keep 住當心情日記咁post 圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\nbtw 巴打個名，係咪睇射雕英雄傳所以改到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係啦，求其改咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得咁都幾好呀，當心靈雞湯咁畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時有圖同埋字句真係講到心坎裏去的話，係冇辦法言喻架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d4e35acecc72dea6342d6f0914c2b42ac1807eb","tid":316474,"uid":75427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T16:45:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係啦，求其改咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得咁都幾好呀，當心靈雞湯咁畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時有圖同埋字句真係講到心坎裏去的話，係冇辦法言喻架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我重以為係李一桐fans , 見到射雕個post 個個人個名都有個桐字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係架，以前我個ig 簡介就係寫住 俾自已嘅心靈雞湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d62bb3f91a920e1cba13d03c904e2bae3098d6fd","tid":316474,"uid":75427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T17:38:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51bf9b89ac4898d1a625da8746377dce20577fbf","tid":316474,"uid":75427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T18:03:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51ba257193f4d1f8bbbfbdb7b0a1c46b9f63b134","tid":316474,"uid":75427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T15:08:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2277ea60b8f0608b9a385cafd41259aa51207d3a","tid":316474,"uid":10292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T15:11:41.000Z","msg":"好可愛"},{"pid":"e88bea09dfab2fa065d7ed100c900d03004fd77b","tid":316474,"uid":75427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T15:45:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好可愛</blockquote><br />\n多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e638f63637c5504578390da60e4aa3a336557547","tid":316474,"uid":73604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T16:41:40.000Z","msg":"又有新作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd23065ffca4c01e30b85ca434e27b3211b2d41e","tid":316474,"uid":75427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T18:55:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又有新作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我三日唔埋兩日就畫"},{"pid":"1ea17e1ba89bab6b557a80b1f18a983c68716b3d","tid":316474,"uid":104474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T20:03:11.000Z","msg":"幾得意啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  巴打用咩畫板？"},{"pid":"8febfa6107f38651321e857fe9c9dd766b0f27e7","tid":316474,"uid":104474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T20:04:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>離一離題 絲打啲人像畫好犀利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好想有你一成功力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係巴打啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n如果想畫人像畫，首先要熟識人頭部結構先，起碼就算畫得唔似但畫出黎都會似一個正常人，乜都唔理剩係照住相片練習成效會冇咁好，畢竟只係copy and paste<br />\n建議睇吓書~ <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.alexhays.com/loomis/Andrew%20Loomis%20-%20Drawing%20the%20Head%20and%20Hands.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.alexhays.com%2Floomis%2FAndrew%2520Loomis%2520-%2520Drawing%2520the%2520Head%2520and%2520Hands.pdf&d=9ky%2BgztbjGp%2BB9QNofxjDAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=aa3ab6d3\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.alexhays.com/loomis/Andrew%20Loomi