,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T06:01:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4254faefb532a0120b250dbca07c819e020c1502","tid":316474,"uid":104474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T09:04:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>幾得意啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  巴打用咩畫板？</blockquote><br />\n好多年前WACOM最入門嗰隻BAMBOO PEN<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一直都冇換過塊畫板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n畫3D野得唔得？"},{"pid":"9897ccc3a3bdf92191ab9f3c7fefd51be84d18e8","tid":316474,"uid":75427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T09:56:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>幾得意啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  巴打用咩畫板？</blockquote><br />\n好多年前WACOM最入門嗰隻BAMBOO PEN<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一直都冇換過塊畫板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n畫3D野得唔得？</blockquote><br />\n畫3d野睇個軟件程式啫，應該都係咁用， btw 我冇做開3d 唔太確定"},{"pid":"5764d8bfff733b545a85c75036d5e59acc1d91db","tid":316474,"uid":75427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T10:34:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3be80b41fb140a903ad53c47e910524ef0605f61","tid":316474,"uid":104474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T10:39:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>幾得意啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  巴打用咩畫板？</blockquote><br />\n好多年前WACOM最入門嗰隻BAMBOO PEN<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一直都冇換過塊畫板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n畫3D野得唔得？</blockquote><br />\n畫3d野睇個軟件程式啫，應該都係咁用， btw 我冇做開3d 唔太確定</blockquote><br />\n我指多啲陰影冇咁cartoon feel個啲畫"},{"pid":"c565a0521441b58032fa4a41719e9ab34028a581","tid":316474,"uid":75427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T11:11:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>幾得意啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  巴打用咩畫板？</blockquote><br />\n好多年前WACOM最入門嗰隻BAMBOO PEN<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一直都冇換過塊畫板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n畫3D野得唔得？</blockquote><br />\n畫3d野睇個軟件程式啫，應該都係咁用， btw 我冇做開3d 唔太確定</blockquote><br />\n我指多啲陰影冇咁cartoon feel個啲畫</blockquote><br />\n可以，嗰啲其實最主要係睇你基本功，如造型結構，透視，用色，等等技巧，不過如果經濟能力許可梗係買好少少，因為一塊都可以用好多年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而且買咗畫唔到你都唔可以拎工具唔夠好黎做藉口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 然後繼續努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  btw 我嗰塊產都停埋了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"811f52ab13e68b82b70d97fa902d94a928c61796","tid":316474,"uid":104474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T14:39:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n原來係巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋想問下你練咗幾多年結構先畫成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我正式學畫畫就三年（唔係專學人像畫），同埋我係知道咗就算，直接應用係我嘅畫上面，所以要答你練咗幾耐結構答唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n結構你睇下我上面本書啲圖，明咗就得，唔睇晒全本書都得，又話者係google 搵人像素描結構之類嘅野睇吓，google 搵藝用解剖又得，但其實我素描能力都好弱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n最主要係理解個結構，所以你會見到啲人學畫人會畫頭骨，又會畫下頭骨+面部肌肉組織，例如知道咗眉骨突，眼窩凹，顴骨突起，咁畫人像嗰時就要用線條/明暗/排線等手法表現到呢啲特點出黎， 然後又要睇啲小結構啦，就好似鼻孔係咪單統畫個圓形就得呢？照鏡睇下自已個鼻，鼻頭同鼻翼之間點樣互相連結呢？ 又例如眼，細心啲睇你會見到上眼簾會包住下眼簾。畫畫隨咗多畫之外，重要多看，睇到先會畫得到</blockquote><br />\n作文寫字 咩都係 先大後小有框架先"},{"pid":"c1b7440595f77a5aa42a8bf3b139c7c805386d9f","tid":316474,"uid":104474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T14:40:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>幾得意啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  巴打用咩畫板？</blockquote><br />\n好多年前WACOM最入門嗰隻BAMBOO PEN<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一直都冇換過塊畫板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n畫3D野得唔得？</blockquote><br />\n畫3d野睇個軟件程式啫，應該都係咁用， btw 我冇做開3d 唔太確定</blockquote><br />\n我指多啲陰影冇咁cartoon feel個啲畫</blockquote><br />\n可以，嗰啲其實最主要係睇你基本功，如造型結構，透視，用色，等等技巧，不過如果經濟能力許可梗係買好少少，因為一塊都可以用好多年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而且買咗畫唔到你都唔可以拎工具唔夠好黎做藉口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 然後繼續努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  btw 我嗰塊產都停埋了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84470046c2c2ea33082b5b8d7d872278b190d992","tid":316474,"uid":75427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T15:44:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n原來係巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋想問下你練咗幾多年結構先畫成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我正式學畫畫就三年（唔係專學人像畫），同埋我係知道咗就算，直接應用係我嘅畫上面，所以要答你練咗幾耐結構答唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n結構你睇下我上面本書啲圖，明咗就得，唔睇晒全本書都得，又話者係google 搵人像素描結構之類嘅野睇吓，google 搵藝用解剖又得，但其實我素描能力都好弱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n最主要係理解個結構，所以你會見到啲人學畫人會畫頭骨，又會畫下頭骨+面部肌肉組織，例如知道咗眉骨突，眼窩凹，顴骨突起，咁畫人像嗰時就要用線條/明暗/排線等手法表現到呢啲特點出黎， 然後又要睇啲小結構啦，就好似鼻孔係咪單統畫個圓形就得呢？照鏡睇下自已個鼻，鼻頭同鼻翼之間點樣互相連結呢？ 又例如眼，細心啲睇你會見到上眼簾會包住下眼簾。畫畫隨咗多畫之外，重要多看，睇到先會畫得到</blockquote><br />\n作文寫字 咩都係 先大後小有框架先</blockquote><br />\n對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2e4595d8df8e5a2626c410be0fe7ed453400cdb","tid":316474,"uid":75427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:34:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"233ab298ec228ba91e856faa692cded735f9eb14","tid":316474,"uid":53947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:54:39.000Z","msg":"有fol你IG<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b9f3555e8c3cb9d6914afb76d6fcd7c60c36759","tid":316474,"uid":75427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T17:43:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有fol你IG<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好unfollow 我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"144dbe1ea152dd5eaed9bb321611c962137cb380","tid":316474,"uid":75427,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T03:33:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"163ce90d30b25201a84780525a77a4c268fa8d0e","tid":316474,"uid":75427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T05:03:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84df13d9d168c349281f66d627b166a3f6c0d14b","tid":316474,"uid":90605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T06:26:01.000Z","msg":"巴打 你隻角色想帶出咩信息"},{"pid":"2aedd67d051cd77ce866f6944e8102e07058ae8f","tid":316474,"uid":75427,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T07:05:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打 你隻角色想帶出咩信息</blockquote><br />\n以個造形黎講，一隻被白布包住嘅鬼仔，永遠冇人見到佢嘅真面目，就好似我地平時嘅心聲唔會話俾人知咁，亦代表潛藏內心真正嘅我，而呢種類似匿名嘅方式，就好似我地係網絡世界因為唔洗露面而可以暢所欲言咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n但如果係入面圖文嘅內容我就冇特定方向，全部都係我自己當日感受，當佢係一個blog 咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1595ef6bf13a4ccb7b74a393cbc75d9f6e3b6a6","tid":316474,"uid":40662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T09:26:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04909aaa5b5f86460fe40b664200dcc0b40a2aff","tid":316474,"uid":75427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T15:39:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6877bf12b40618aee4c88566314d4ca0a20030e","tid":316474,"uid":75427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T16:33:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dbcd4b3576f47858508816c553d301eb3606b72","tid":316474,"uid":75427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T17:59:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}